c: 13
v: 11
t: "Aliyense ali ndi angelo amene amakhala patsogolo ndi pambuyo pake. Iwo amamuyang’anira iye potsatira malamulo a Mulungu. Ndithudi! Mulungu sadzasintha chikhalidwe cha anthu pokhapokha iwo eni ake asintha makhalidwe awo. Koma ngati Mulungu afuna kulanga anthu, palibe amene angathawe ndipo iwo sadzapeza wina kupatula Iye amene angawateteze"